      <title>镍危机后 LME 将清算会员资本需求增加三倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/lme-to-triple-clearer-capital-needs-in-post-nickel-crisis-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所 (LME) 清算所计划将会员资本要求提高两倍，这是旨在两年多前镍价出现空头挤压危机后强化市场的最新改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/lme-to-triple-clearer-capital-needs-in-post-nickel-crisis-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 16:33:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
